To test the significance of sex on the structure volumes, we fit two models. Model 1 contains fixed effects sex s and time point τk (where k goes from 1 to 9 for each of our experimental time points), as well as interaction terms. Model 1 also had a random intercept for each individual mouse βi. Based on the general equation (1), the formula for Model 1 is given below:4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
